div.p:

mithyājñānaṃ vicikitsā mānaḥ pramāda iti/ trairāśyān
                           nopasaṅkhyāyante iti/ lakṣaṇasya tarhy abhedāt tritvam anupapannam?
                           nānupapannam, rāgadveṣamohārthāntarabhāvāt;

yatrānekasya padasya vākyasya vā paurvāparyeṇānvayayogo nāstīty
                           asambaddhārthatvagṛhyte, tat samudāyārthasyāpāyād apārthakam/ yathā ---
                           daśa dāḍimāni, ṣaḍ apūpāḥ;
